title: Christina
content: It was love at first sight. When seventeen-year-old Arnie saw Christina, he realized: they must belong to each other. However, the others did not share his delight. Best friend, Dennis, immediately became suspicious of Christine. A friend, the first school beauty, was jealous of Arnie for Christina and was afraid of her. But soon both relatives and enemies of Arnie will understand what happens if you cross Christinas road. Because Christina is not a girl, but a death machine generated by Evil ...

title: Nature news
content: Noise from shipping, construction, sonar and seismic surveys is "drowning out" the healthy ocean soundscape, scientists say.

title: Black Or White
content: The eighth child of the Jackson family, Jackson made his professional debut in 1964 with his elder brothers Jackie, Tito, Jermaine, and Marlon as a member of the Jackson 5. Jackson began his solo career in 1971 while at Motown Records, and rose to solo stardom with his fifth studio album Off the Wall (1979) during the peak of the disco era
